Package: fbicrime
Type: Package
Title: R wrapper for FBI Crime API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Wenjun', 'Sun', email = 'sunwenjun97@gmail.com', role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: FBI, Federal Bureau of Investigation, provides offense, offenders, victim, arrest data 
    for the United States through an API named FBI Crime Data API. 
    The fbicrime package package provides an R wrapper for the API, so that R users can directly 
    access the most updated crime data from R.
    See <https://crime-data-explorer.fr.cloud.gov/api> for the FBI Crime Data API description.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    httr,
    jsonlite
